{
  "stem": "1895.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 343.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one was my mother's brother-in-law, a-- a-- a gentleman, [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Eric ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Rothsfeld. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they-- they survived the initial resettlements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were both in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were later selected.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the people who were older, people who were weak, people who were-- you know, they kept selecting, taking them out, and shooting them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Taking them out, and shooting them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, people who couldn't provide them with the services that they needed were completely unnecessary and removed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the existence of the people of the 3,000 in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As far as my fate was concerned, I stayed in the munitions factory, and I completely deteriorated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And primarily I deteriorated because life was not worth living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I felt terrible guilt pangs, and I stopped caring about my appearance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I showed all the signs of going, which was commonplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Other people showed it, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't want to see or talk to anybody that knew me before, or that I knew before.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was ashamed of the way I looked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was ashamed-- I-- I-- I just didn't want to go on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I had no reason to go on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I lost completely the will to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But then, one day, one of my friends, who remained among the 3,000, sent me a note through a Jewish auxiliary, who was a liaison between the ghetto-- the remaining ghetto, and the munitions factory.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this fellow looked me up, and he handed me the note.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And in the note, my friend, Moniek Ackerman told me that he heard that I was down and out, and that he wants to help me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he told me to make an attempt, an escape from the munitions factory into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
